==Description==
Brune is a Rabbibunny who works at the [[Ticket shop (Citadel Island)|Ticket shop]]. She has two kids: the rabbibunny pupil and the [[Umbrella thief|thief]] of the [[umbrella]].

==Role in Twinsen's adventure==
Like most characters, Brune's only role was to give [[Twinsen]] some hints. In her case, it was about finding [[Raph]] the [[lighthouse]] keeper.

